channel.title: [PI] Java/Client Developer
channel.description:
I am looking for java, client, or website developer that has experience in one of this fields. Right now, I have a source that I have been coding for sometime, the revision is 317 with 508+ data added. I have redone and made improvements to the mini-games in which in my opinion is about 85-90% completed, just need to be re-look at and improved in my standards and the others behave. My overall improvement that I have been working on where relocating npc's, shops, home, spawns, small bugs, adding items, mini-games, clipping, specials, dupes and etc. The client is alright but going to need a bit changed, I have also jared and signed the client but think about using a different one, Don't know yet. Also been have trouble of thinking of a name but that's easy. If you have NO or SMALL experience on I will require you to do something else to be part of the team but If you are experience with one of the two contract me on Skype for more information.
Skype: c2dahizzy
